 :tx/rationale "Create task: EPIC: Session Trajectory — first-class session lifecycle with cross-session convergence tracking. BACKGROUND: The session lifecycle is asymmetric: harvest marks the END but nothing marks the BEGINNING. This breaks F(S) delta display (SD-1), session-scoped M(t) accuracy, and cross-session convergence verification. Sessions form an adjunction (Agent attention ⊣ Store state) where seed = unit and harvest = counit. The session monad is incomplete without a 'return' operation (session start). APPROACH: Make the session trajectory a first-class store entity. Auto-detect session start (first command after gap), record initial state, sample trajectory points, finalize at harvest. Ring-buffer last 20 sessions for trend analysis. ENABLES: (1) F(S) delta from session start, (2) M(t) scoped to actual session, (3) cross-session Lyapunov certificate, (4) session-level R(t) learning, (5) trajectory-aware seed. TRACES TO: INV-BILATERAL-001, INV-HARVEST-001, INV-SEED-001, INV-GUIDANCE-021."
